Module PartOne
Package objectclasses

Class Competitor

java.lang.Object
objectclasses.Competitor
public class Competitor extends Object
The Competitor class is used to represent the details of a given competitor. It stores and provides methods to access and modify the competitor details, such as their name, age, country and scores.
Version:
1.0
